* Dinobot growled, just another ploy to get their guard down then stab them 
in the back no doubt! He didn't like it, but then he wasn't the one who 
called the shots around here.
He growled again then dug his claw into the surface of the table...*

" So, we not only have to watch our backs on the battle field but in the 
Base as well?!"

* He had no idea why Liono would let such a bot into their ranks but he knew 
one thing for sure, if that bot even came near Tavatron or himself he'd 
squish 'em! Dinobot had learned one very important thing while he fought in 
the earlier Beast Wars, never trust an arachnid! Especially one that was 
cloned from Tarantulus himself!
He sank his claw deeper into the metal of the table, what was this planet 
coming to?*
